view

Class ViewGeneric

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Scene
      • view.ViewGeneric
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Subject, javafx.event.EventTarget
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FacultyView, LoginView, StudentView

    public abstract class ViewGeneric
extends javafx.scene.Scene
implements Subject
    This is an abstract class that plays the role of scene control for the many different views that are presented throughout the program. It extends Scene to allow for interchanging of scenes, and implements subject to be able to be used by the observer, to allow for MVC
